This directory contains Libgcrypt's default implementation of the
secmem subsystem.  When built, this subsystem will be put into a
library named `libgcrypt-secmem.la'.

This subsystem contains a simple, heap-based memory manager, which is
supposed to meet the needs of secure  ... FIXME

Files:

  core.c: core functionality.
  interface.c: public interface on top of core functionality.
  gcrypt-secmem-common.h: internal and public definitions.
  gcrypt-secmem-internal.h: internal definitions.
  gcrypt-secmem.h: public definitions.
